    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even about expectations though. it's just... nothing. i'm just a ghost in a costume. it's exhausting to keep pretending to be a person when the person is already gone. how am i supposed to \"re-evaluate\" something that isn't even there?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
